# Drop these files here before running `npm run icons`:
#
#   icon.png       — 1024×1024 (round corners drawn by Android)
#   splash.png     — 2732×2732 (centered logo on background)
#
# Then:
#   npm run icons
#   npx cap sync android
#
# Capacitor Assets will generate the mdpi → xxxhdpi mipmap variants
# and place them under android/app/src/main/res/.
